cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

The paper deals with image restoration using deep CNN denoiser prior, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The paper also involves training CNNs using discriminative learning, which is a sub-field of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper uses convolutional neural networks (CNNs) for image restoration, which is a sub-field of multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, the paper involves optimization techniques, which is a sub-field of neural networks (cs.NE).
